# @hivork/api — environment variables (subset)
#
# Source of truth: ../../.env.example (repo root)
#
# Setup (recommended):
#   cp ../../.env.example ../../.env
#
# NestJS ConfigModule (TASK-006) loads from repo root .env.
# Override locally with apps/api/.env.local if needed (gitignored).
#
# Required for this app:
#   DATABASE_URL
#   REDIS_URL
#   JWT_ACCESS_SECRET, JWT_REFRESH_SECRET
#   JWT_ACCESS_TTL, JWT_REFRESH_TTL, JWT_REFRESH_SESSION_TTL
#   CAPTCHA_ENABLED, CAPTCHA_PROVIDER, CAPTCHA_SECRET_KEY, CAPTCHA_SITE_KEY, CAPTCHA_BYPASS_TOKEN
#   OTP_TTL_SECONDS, OTP_RATE_LIMIT_PER_MINUTE
#   API_PORT (default 4000)
#   LOG_LEVEL
#   CORS_ORIGIN
#
# See ../../.env.example for full list and documentation.
